_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldStatistics/Basic.html#FieldStatistic.bosonic\">bosonic</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a> <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldStatistics/Basic.html#FieldStatistic.bosonic\">bosonic</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldStatistics/Basic.html#FieldStatistic.bosonic\">bosonic</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldStatistics/Basic.html#FieldStatistic.bosonic_mul_bosonic","kind":"theorem","line":59,"name":"FieldStatistic.bosonic_mul_bosonic","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L59-L60"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldStatistics/Basic.html#FieldStatistic.instCommGroup\"><span class=\"name\">FieldStatistic</span>.<span class=\"name\">instCommGroup</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#CommGroup\">CommGroup</a> <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldStatistics/Basic.html#FieldStatistic\">FieldStatistic</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The type `FieldStatistic` carries an instance of a commutative group in which\n- `bosonic * bosonic = bosonic`\n- `bosonic * fermionic = fermionic`\n- `fermionic * bosonic = fermionic`\n- `fermionic * fermionic = bosonic`\n\nThis group is isomorphic to `ℤ₂`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldStatistics/Basic.html#FieldStatistic.instCommGroup","kind":"instance","line":30,"name":"FieldStatistic.instCommGroup","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L30-L57"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldStatistics/Basic.html#instDecidableEqFieldStatistic\"><span class=\"name\">instDecidableEqFieldStatistic</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#DecidableEq\">DecidableEq</a> <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldStatistics/Basic.html#FieldStatistic\">FieldStatistic</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldStatistics/Basic.html#instDecidableEqFieldStatistic","kind":"instance","line":24,"name":"instDecidableEqFieldStatistic","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L24-L24"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldStatistics/Basic.html#FieldStatistic.fermionic\"><span class=\"name\">FieldStatistic</span>.<span class=\"name\">fermionic</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldStatistics/Basic.html#FieldStatistic\">FieldStatistic</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldStatistics/Basic.html#FieldStatistic.fermionic","kind":"ctor","line":23,"name":"FieldStatistic.fermionic","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L23-L23"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldStatistics/Basic.html#FieldStatistic.bosonic\"><span class=\"name\">FieldStatistic</span>.<span class=\"name\">bosonic</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldStatistics/Basic.html#FieldStatistic\">FieldStatistic</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldStatistics/Basic.html#FieldStatistic.bosonic","kind":"ctor","line":22,"name":"FieldStatistic.bosonic","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L22-L22"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">inductive</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldStatistics/Basic.html#FieldStatistic\"><span class=\"name\">FieldStatistic</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The type `FieldStatistic` is the type containing two elements `bosonic` and `fermionic`.\nThis type is used to specify if a field or operator obeys bosonic or fermionic statistics. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldStatistics/Basic.html#FieldStatistic","kind":"inductive","line":19,"name":"FieldStatistic","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L19-L24"}}],"imports":["Init","PhysLean.Mathematics.List.InsertIdx","Mathlib.Tactic.FinCases","Mathlib.Algebra.BigOperators.Group.Finset.Piecewise","Mathlib.Data.Fintype.Card","Mathlib.Algebra.FreeMonoid.Basic"],"instances":[{"className":"Decidable","name":"instDecidableEqFieldStatistic","typeNames":["Eq"]},{"className":"CommGroup","name":"FieldStatistic.instCommGroup","typeNames":["FieldStatistic"]},{"className":"Fintype","name":"FieldStatistic.instFintype","typeNames":["FieldStatistic"]},{"className":"AddMonoid","name":"FieldStatistic.instAddMonoid","typeNames":["FieldStatistic"]}],"name":"PhysLean.QFT.PerturbationTheory.FieldStatistics.Basic"}